question: Boca Juniors kah Estudiantes de La Plata, hit e-ke tuí tī 2008 nî Copa Sudamericana pí-sài, hit e-ke khah chhut-sek, sī-ūi?
answer: Estudiantes de La Plata pí-sài khah chhut-sek. In kàu final, tit 'Runner up', nā-sī Boca Juniors tī 'Quarterfinals' hō͘ kā-tńg-khì.

question: Chit e siaⁿ-mih tūi-á tī 2008 nî Copa Sudamericana hō͘ Estudiantes de La Plata só͘ phah-sak?
2008 年 Recopa Sudamericana 冠軍隊伍，對手是佗一隊？
Estudiantes de La Plata tī 2008 nî ê Copa Sudamericana kah 2009 nî ê Copa Libertadores ê pí-sài, pún-sin ê piáu-hiān ū sím-mi̍h kái-piàn?
answer: Estudiantes de La Plata ê piáu-hiān tōa-tāi kái-chìn. In tī 2008 nî ê Copa Sudamericana tit tio̍h 'Runner up', āu-lâi tī 2009 nî ê Copa Libertadores chiâⁿ-chò 'Champions'.

question: Lia̍t-chhut só͘-ū chham-ka 2008 nî Copa Sudamericana, m̄-koh bô-hoat-tō͘ chìn-ji̍p 2009 nî Copa Libertadores ê tūi-ngó͘.
Chia̍h-pō͘ pún-téng, tī chia lia̍t-chhut ê pí-sài, ū kúi-chiah tūi-ngó͘ tit-tio̍h chi̍t-ê kà-chheng?
Nā-chún 2008 nî Recopa Sudamericana koat-sài ê kiat-kó kā-hoāⁿ-hoāⁿ, Boca Juniors tī cell C3 ê kì-lio̍k ē chiâⁿ-chò siáⁿ-mi̍h?
answer: Nā-chún kiat-kó kā-hoāⁿ-hoāⁿ, Boca Juniors ê kì-lio̍k ē iû 'Champions defeated Arsenal de Sarandí' kái-piàn chò 'Runner up lost to Arsenal de Sarandí'.

question: Chit-ê tō-lí piáu-bīn ū bô kóng-bêng 2008 nî tit-tio̍h koan-kun ê tūi-ngó͘ kap 2009 nî Copa Libertadores ê chìn-ji̍p chi-kan ū liân-soà?
answer: Bô, chit-ê tō-lí piáu-bīn bô kóng-bêng tō-ē-tàng liân-soà. Tī 2008 nî tit-tio̍h koan-kun ê nn̄g-ê tūi-ngó͘ tiong, Arsenal de Sarandí bô chìn-ji̍p 2009 nî Copa Libertadores, m̄-koh Boca Juniors iūⁿ. Chit-ê 50/50 ê hun-pò͘, tùi chi̍t-ê chin-chió ê sū-kiāⁿ-lu̍t lâi-khòaⁿ, bô-hoat-tō͘ lâi thui-chhek ū liân-soà.

question: Sui chiá-pí-sài liân-miâ, tsuè-tsē tshut-hiān sio-siâng ê kiat-kó (i.e., tsuè-tōa ê tsi̍t-ê teh sîng-kong ia̍h-sī khuán-tû ê tiān-huè)?
Sui e-ê tui-á ê kiat-kó tī kui-ê pió-á lāi-té, tī kēng-ki-á ê sêng-chiū hong-bīn siōng-kài tòng-sìng ê chi̍t-ê?
answer: Estudiantes de La Plata tī 2009 nî ê Copa Libertadores ê sèng-lī sī siōng-kài tòng-sìng ê chi̍t-ê. Tû-liáu kî-thaⁿ tui-á mā iâⁿ tio̍h kûn-thâu, iâⁿ Copa Libertadores sī pió-á lāi-té siōng-kài koân-téng ê sêng-chiū, hō͘ in tī hit-ê kēng-ki-á lāi-té ê 'Champions' tē-ūi, kap kî-thaⁿ ê kiat-kó pí-kàu, pau-koah kî-thaⁿ ê kûn-thâu, lóng khah chhut-thâu.
